nodes.text: Primitive Sentient Protection and Alliance, Operation 265-A: Karra

Primitive Sentient Protection and Alliance, Operation 265-A: Karra was the designation of an Alliance to Restore the Republic mission to the planet Karra to broker an alliance with the native Karran. It was headed by Doctor Elth Nardah, and assisted by Karvinna Raen and a team of Alliance agents.
